Package: prospectr
Type: Package
Title: Miscellaneous functions for processing and sample selection of vis-NIR
    diffuse reflectance data
Version: 0.1.3
Date: 2013-12-11
Author: Antoine Stevens and Leonardo Ramirez-Lopez
Maintainer: Antoine Stevens <antoine.stevens@uclouvain.be>
